[[File:Soldier (Shayzien) chathead.png|left]]
'''Soldiers''' are members of the [[Shayzien Army]] found in the [[Shayzien Encampment]]. They have identical stats and drops to regular [[Guard (Shayzien)|guards]], but cannot be pickpocketed

They appear to be wearing a [[black scimitar]] and a [[black kiteshield]]. They have a tougher version, their [[Sergeant (Shayzien)|sergeant]].

